# Keep local ARCHS4 data and checkpoints out of GitHub while retaining folder docs.
archs4/**
!archs4/
!archs4/README.md
!archs4/**/
!archs4/**/README.md

# ARCHS4 evaluation artifacts are intended to be publishable when they are
# below the repository size limit. Git cannot enforce the 90 MB threshold, so
# keep any future larger evaluation artifact out of Git or put it in Git LFS.
!archs4/evaluation/**
